recipe: Database ( TAP_Core_Data ) | Query ( "SELECT DISTINCT (SAMPLE(?System) AS ?sys) (SAMPLE(?owner) AS ?Owner) (COALESCE(COUNT(DISTINCT(?ICD)), 0) AS ?SystemInterfaceCount) WHERE { {?System <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem>;}  {?owner <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SystemOwner>;} {?System <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/OwnedBy> ?owner } BIND(URI(CONCAT(STR(?System),STR(?owner))) AS ?sysOwner) OPTIONAL{ BIND(<http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide> AS ?Upstream) {?ICD <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SystemInterface> ;} {?System ?Upstream ?ICD ;} } } GROUP BY ?sysOwner" ) | Import ( ) ;

Frame ( ) | Select ( f$ sys , f$ Owner , f$ SystemInterfaceCount ) | Format ( type = [ 'table' ] ) | TaskOptions ( { '0' : { "layout" : "Grid" , "alignment" : { "label" : [ "sys" , "Owner" , "SystemInterfaceCount" ] } } } ) | Collect ( 500 ) ;
